                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>General aspects of the war in Europe are included in this section. Papers,
                    however, which deal exclusively with Italian questions (e.g., peace feelers,
                    surrender terms, and the status of Rome as an open city) and with the question
                    of bases in the Azores are printed in separate sections below.</p>
            </div>
